OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with some sunny intervals.
OL,7,FThere will be some clear spells at
OL,8,Ffirst tonight but clouding over,
OL,9,Fperhaps a light shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FIt will be a cloudier day,
OL,12,Fperhaps with the odd shower, but it
OL,13,Fshould brighten up later in the day
OL,14,Fwith some warm sunnier spells.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,17,Fand very warm few days with some sunny
OL,18,Fspells. Perhaps some thundery showers
OL,19,Flater on Thursday
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
